{"tid":205801,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 整電腦地獄 好撚辛苦大佬","createTime":"2017-04-18T05:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T06:38:50.000Z","uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"115e9e0c658579606abb65a2f49c44233ce02984","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"[求救] 話說之前電腦個畫面開始花, 慢慢變到無畫面, 連bios畫面都花呢花碌<br />\n咁我以為板壞 就換晒板 cpu ram 牛都換埋  是關d野都幾舊下<br />\n姐係舊嘅野依家得返display同hard disk<br />\n之後我一開機 load左一陣都入唔到windows 慢慢仲聞到小小燒膠味<br />\n跟住約略check過底板d 電容又無爆<br />\n之後淨係無插hard disk再開 又入到bios cpu溫度呀 ram呀一切正常  無味無臭<br />\n跟住就無深究到係邊度出燒膠味 要早訓第朝返工<br />\n<br />\n我想問呢個case係邊度出問題居多 [已有準備收工去買埋hard disk/ display]"},{"pid":"63ce122b23bc69c88adda0db6c47dc75f12321f6","tid":205801,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"Harddisk/火牛 是旦一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076e6a403764535e9962d701ce29f4cc4a097db2","tid":205801,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"唔一次過換晒 結果又搞死埋新野真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"66e067d1c1c0280511333953c95d9d49598abe5b","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔一次過換晒 結果又搞死埋新野真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n唉  啱呀<br />\n屌鳩晒d display hard disk  所有硬件嘅老母"},{"pid":"21f71c999bae4950591ef66c674a5a2b19f368ae","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Harddisk/火牛 是旦一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望d膠味係由hard disk出<br />\n新買隻牛又爛我屌化隻hard disk"},{"pid":"094bd1379f0a41c10a195eeede2629b34f662a6b","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:21:49.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係收工已經攰到閪<br />\n仲要同佢玩偵探遊戲"},{"pid":"0cf39dbffef17a5bfd736376b3747ca7693f209c","tid":205801,"uid":17835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚慘係收工已經攰到閪<br />\n仲要同佢玩偵探遊戲</blockquote><br />\n唔想攰就今晚一次買過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087e3082fb3e80debd3c76ad74c38b8c4168174d","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最撚慘係收工已經攰到閪<br />\n仲要同佢玩偵探遊戲</blockquote><br />\n唔想攰就今晚一次買過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收工食埋個飯就去買啦...呢d錢真係唔慳得<br />\n唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5078c464d8abb3ad1eba23b612dde5e5232a4f3a","tid":205801,"uid":91165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"話說之前電腦個畫面開始花, 慢慢變到無畫面, 連bios畫面都花呢花碌<br />\n咁我以為板壞 就換晒板 cpu ram 牛都換埋 是關d野都幾舊下<br />\n姐係舊嘅野依家得返display同hard disk<br />\n之後我一開機 load左一陣都入唔到windows 慢慢仲聞到小小燒膠味<br />\n跟住約略check過底板d 電容又無爆<br />\n之後淨係無插hard disk再開 又入到bios cpu溫度呀 ram呀一切正常 無味無臭<br />\n跟住就無深究到係邊度出燒膠味 要早訓第朝返工<br />\n<br />\n我想問呢個case係邊度出問題居多 [已有準備收工去買埋hard disk/ display]<br />\n<br />\n之前電腦個畫面開始花, 慢慢變到無畫面, 連bios畫面都花呢花碌&lt;-好明顯display card 問題, 你試下蚊走張display card, 用底板onboard display 煲下佢睇下有冇膠味, 如果仲有就建議你成部換算(如果怕辛苦)"},{"pid":"d2cba3a35b60bdbe273b70958444159850b16a74","tid":205801,"uid":17835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最撚慘係收工已經攰到閪<br />\n仲要同佢玩偵探遊戲</blockquote><br />\n唔想攰就今晚一次買過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收工食埋個飯就去買啦...呢d錢真係唔慳得<br />\n唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實可以逐個換同慢慢試<br />\n但我諗你唔想用咁既時間<br />\n當upgrade 啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60025449cc215690abe8e811b5a8caf893df6418","tid":205801,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime